				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12113156#post-4292731</guid>
				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12113156/scp-4251#post-4292731</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2019 17:46:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>pxdnbluesoul</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1414125</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Really dig this from a meta/conceptual standpoint. No attempt is made in the work to figure out what's causing the gravity or lack thereof, and we are diverted neatly into a strikingly realistic set of logs. I like some of the new conventions here in the logs as well.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
